        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:1:36:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/31/1",
        "text": [
          " : \"لاَ تَشْهَدَنَّ عَلَى شَهَادَةٍ حَتَّى تَعْرِفَهَا كَمَا تَعْرِفُ كَفَّكَ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.3359 - It is narrated from Ali ibn Ghurab, from Abu Abdillah (as):\nImam (as) said: \"Do not testify to a testimony until you know it as clearly as you know your own palm.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1914,
        "local_index": 2,
        "narrator_chain": {
          "parts": [
            {
              "kind": "plain",
