              "text": " عَنْ "
            },
            {
              "kind": "narrator",
              "path": "/people/narrators/647",
              "text": "عَلِيِّ بْنِ سُوَيْدٍ"
            },
            {
              "kind": "plain",
              "text": " قَالَ"
            }
          ]
        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:3:1:36:2",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/31/2",
        "text": [
          " : قُلْتُ لِأَبِي اَلْحَسَنِ اَلْمَاضِي عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يُشْهِدُنِي هَؤُلاَءِ عَلَى إِخْوَانِي قَالَ \"نَعَمْ أَقِمِ اَلشَّهَادَةَ لَهُمْ وَ إِنْ خِفْتَ عَلَى أَخِيكَ ضَرَراً \"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.3360 - It is narrated from Ali ibn Suwayd, who said:\nI said to Abu al-Hasan al-Madhi (as) (Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as)): \"These people call me to testify against my brothers.\"\nImam (as) said: 'Yes, establish the testimony for them, even if you fear harm for your brother.'\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1915,
